        "sender_full_name": "Scott Morrison",
        "timestamp": 1621473699
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I see there is <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/set_has_maximal_iff_noetherian/src\">src#set_has_maximal_iff_noetherian</a>.</p>",
